criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Women with overweight or obesity (BMI above 25);

          -  Enrolled in nutritional treatment for weight loss in primary care units and Hospitals
             from Coimbra

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Binge Eating Disorder assessed through Eating Disorders Examination Interview;

          -  Severe psychiatric problems (severe depressive episode, substance abuse, Bipolar
             disorder and Borderline Personality Disorder) assessed through Structured Clinical
             Interview for DSM Disorders (SCDI-I and SCID-II);

          -  medical conditions that affect weight;

          -  medication that can cause significant weight or appetite changes.
